lead_paragraph: The collapse of a temporary ramp at the Rio de Janeiro Olympic sailing venue is not expected to affect competition or training during the Games, the International Olympic Committee (IOC) said on Sunday.

headline.print_headline: Ramp Damage No Concern for Competition-IOC
